channel.title: 317 Cache not found creativescape
channel.description: Hello everyone, I just started using the creativescape source and already stumled upon a problem, after turning into a webclient, first it worked a few times, then I said error loading creativescape, couldn't find cache, THe weird thing is the cache is there, and when I reunpack it in my cache folder, then it works for 1 time and after that it again stops working! Can someone help me with this, I saw this also happens to other peeps using creativescape, If you need pictures of it, then just tell me, thanks
